high_descs: turn around to the right go forward towards the black table
pick up the remote control from the table
turn around to the left go forward towards the black chair
put the remote control on top of the black chair
turn around to the right go forward face the black coffee table
pick up another remote control from the black coffee table
turn to the right go left forward
put the other remote control on top of the black chair
anns.task_desc: put 2 remote controls on top of the black chair

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the chair, then turn left and walk over to the table the television is on.
Pick up the remote off of the table in front of you.
Turn around and walk up to the coffee table, then turn right and walk up to the chair with the credit card on its seat.
Place the remote on the front right edge of the chair seat.
Turn around and walk to the far edge of the coffee table.
Pick up the remote off of the coffee table.
Walk back over to the chair with the remote and red credit card on its seat.
Put the remote on the front left edge of the chair seat.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the television.
Pick up the remote that is below the television.
Turn left and go to the chair on the right.
Put the remote on the right side of the chair.
Turn around, go across the room and turn right to face the black table.
Pick up the remote from the table.
Go back across the room to the chair on the right.
Put the remote on the left side of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on the chair.
